                                            "Parameters": {
                                                "IsHtml": true,
                                                "Text": "<b><font color=\"#9769ED\" size=6>LGBT National Hotline</font></b><br /><br />The LGBT National Hotline provides free, confidential support for callers dealing with sexual orientation or gender identity issues, including coming out issues and relationship concerns. Hours of operation can be found on their site. Call 888-843-4564 to speak to a trained LGBTQIA+ volunteer. <br /><br /><a href=\"https://lgbthotline.org/national-hotline/\">https://lgbthotline.org/national-hotline/</a><br /><br /><br /><br />"
